node.text:
Don’t be cheap when it comes to your ammo. I always tell people that the best way to train is to use what you’re going to use in the real world. In the event you need to use your concealed carry weapon and save your life or the lives of others, you want to make sure you’re familiar with your gear. 

For more information click the link below to find out more about ammo and concealed carry. 

@uscca 
#uscca 
Uscca.com/timkennedy

node.title: Ammo and Gear selection for training

node.text: It might look like I’m a hoarder but I promise you it’s a revolving door of ammo coming in my door and then coming out of my weapons. node.text: The balance between dangerous freedom and peaceful slavery is more vulnerable than ever before. The beauty that is America. The beauty that is our freedom. The beauty that is our People and American spirit. The brilliance that is our Constitution is and has always been an imperfect system that is only made possible by individual responsibility. Our elections are part of this system. I’ve spent much of my adult life working in counterterrorism and in a counterinsurgency role. We, the US Army Special Forces, have trained insurgents and have fought them in various theaters around the globe. With Joe, I use a metaphor about how a single person, under financed, has the capability of destroying an event(election). If you don’t think that our enemies (China and Russia) are funding, supporting, and stoking the fires of hate to further divide our nation you have to be either naïve or an idiot. We currently are in a conflict and their method of war is economic and a social/cultural one.

node.text: When things get kind of crazy I either want to join in the fun or understand why people have lost their minds. In this case there are a bunch of idiots lobbing unfounded accusations at a few of my friends.  @evanhafer @mat_best_official and @jtarticle15 are first and foremost patriots. I may not like how popular they are or how devilishly good looking Mat is but I know for a fact that they try every waking minutes moment of the day to expand freedom and protect the Constitution. Anyone that says otherwise is either a liar or ignorant. We’re talking about a special forces officer, a former army ranger, and an Air Force special operations nerd. I think it is despicable and shameful what people are doing insane right now. We are better than this. We can either fight united or lose divided. Everyone of you that is participating in spreading false rumors is contributing to the divide.  Grow up! Learn how to stand with and defend the men and women that put themselves out there.

We are in the final stages of opening the first Apogee School in Austin, Texas and need some help. Support our school as we build our private library with ALL books that any young hero might want to read. We also are setting up scholarships for heroes of ALL family and economic backgrounds. Donate today and help us build our next generation with unlimited potential. Go to our website and click Donate. We are organized as a for-profit business, a private school, and childcare/preschool. We are organized this way to minimize any form of governance or oversight.
I will personally match all your donations to ensure the ultimate success for these heroes! At Apogee Cedar Park we are able to make our own choices and changes in our learning environment for the betterment of our children and families because we operate as a private institution. Our students are nurtured in well-rounded and loving campuses, their small class learning Studios ensure they get the attention they need, and they develop lifelong friendships with other like-minded young heroes.
Go to our website https://apogeecedarpark.org/donate link in bio click Donate. You can donate by check or card online. 
I will personally match all your donations to ensure the ultimate success for these heroes! Follow @apogeecedarpark

node.text: Bullets are fast. They are also kind of assholes. I don't want to wear anything that's supposed to stop bullets without putting it through a few field tests. These @guarddogbodyarmor plates held up against our standard stress test and then they go above and beyond with us  throwing the new military M855A1 rounds at it. When it comes to keeping blood in my body I normally don't like the idea of being cheap, but these plates held their own. I give it a SUSTAIN. This is not a lab test.

node.text: After further inspection/interrogation it was discovered that my one year-old gained access to my office, found my match grade ammo of 7.62 , and thought it was important to provide the same substance/nutrients that she consumes to my bullets.

node.title: Babies, bullets, and bottles don’t mix.

node.text: I love this country. I love this flag. I love our National Anthem. I love me some freedom. We might feel further apart than ever before but even with that in mind we have something special. We have something different. We have something that has never existed in the history of civilization. It’s not an easy thing to have so don’t let it go. Give me dangerous freedom.

node.text:
I really liked what Kyle Dake said in his Flo interview after placing 3rd in the olympics when he was expecting 1st. 

He was asked why he wasn’t 100% day one and what went wrong in his quarterfinal match. He said it was not the weight cut. But did not want to go any further. 

He didn’t want to make an excuse for what he thought was a subpar performance.  But when pressed on it he said something great. 

“if you can’t win in an imperfect circumstance you are not good enough to win it.  If everything has to be perfect then you have to get better”.

node.text:
Empower your immunity. 
We as humans are an incredible and powerful species. If we empower the human body to adapt, strengthen, and fortify itself, there is no telling what diseases we could erase off the face of our planet. 

Without question, the leading causes of death in the United States are Heart Disease and Cancer. Americans are fat and getting fatter. We are becoming more and more obese year after year, which has been trending upwards for the past 60 years. Weight and BMI are the leading cause of heart disease, cancer, and also increase the risk of severe illness and symptoms from COVID-19. It is our fault we are in this position. It is our fault we have become such a vulnerable society. 

One of the most dangerous rhetorics of the past decade has been that the most deadly threat to the human body is a diminutive and dinky disease. Still, I do everything I can to naturally strengthen my immune system so that if I do get sick, my body is already prepared and has the strength to fight back. 

Do your part to protect yourself, AND America. BE HEALTHY. Exercise each day, eat real and healthy foods, do martial arts, hunt if you can, go play outside. Hell, lick a couple door handles if you want to add some extra pathogens to your arsenal for adaptation. Have some candle light sexy time, followed by a great night of restorative sleep. Believe in real science, strengthen your body, and start living a healthy life now. #health #fitness #science

Don’t be cheap when it comes to your ammo. I always tell people that the best way to train is to use what you’re going to use in the real world. In the event you need to use your concealed carry weapon and save your life or the lives of others, you want to make sure you’re familiar with your gear.

node.text:
Hero and selfless servant Police Officer Ella French was murdered last night. She was 29 years old. 

She was ambushed and gunned down last night in Chicago. Every department in the nation needs our support. They need more training. They need more personal. They need The People to stand up against the policies that are destroying our cities. Say her name. Pray for Ella French’s family. She is the 194th police officer to die in the line of duty this year.
